Package: metisotopes
Type: Package
Title: Isotope Analysis and Manipulation
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Phil Seitzer
Maintainer: Phil Seitzer <phillipseitzer@calicolabs.com>
Description: Convenience functions for analyzing / processing isotopic envelopes.
    Relies on many of the isotopic functionality in maven_core, which
    is exposed to R via the Rcpp_isotopes.cpp file in mzkitcpp.
